comments: Fox (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Gay (SAS).
RAR shows Fox (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from DeRozan (SAS).  Any ensuing body contact after the ball is deflected is considered incidental.
Barnes (SAC) briefly places his hands on DeRozan's (SAS) body but removes them without affecting DeRozan's ability to move towards the inbound pass.
LLS shows DeRozan (SAS) makes contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
RLS and RLB show Aldridge (SAS) legally contests Barnes' (SAC) shot near the rim and makes incidental contact to Barnes' arm after he has released his shot attempt.
RAR shows Fox (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Mills (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
LAR shows Forbes (SAS) is already in Barnes' (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
MOB shows Barnes (SAC) and Aldridge (SAS) engage then disengage before Barnes cleanly deflects the ball away from Aldridge.
LLB shows Forbes (SAS) makes contact to Cauley-Stein's (SAC) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) and Forbes (SAS) briefly engage and disengage after the legal screen.
Forbes (SAS) is already in Cauley-Stein's (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Aldridge (SAS) slides his pivot foot.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Aldridge (SAS) in the post.
DeRozan (SAS) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (SAC) legally contests Belinelli's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Mills (SAS) attempts to commit a take foul on Hield (SAC), but the contact is marginal and Hield spins off of the contact.
Belinelli (SAS) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
[Observable in enhanced video] Mills (SAS) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
